WARNING!!!!

The plugin no longer works on iOS 7, it will retunr a dummy value 20:00:00:00:00:00, it's no longer possible to get the MAC address on iOS 7.



The code from

http://iosdevelopertips.com/device/determine-mac-address.html

It returns the wifi MAC address even if it is turned off or the user is using a cellular network:

There is a sample project and the sample code inside the index.html


How to use:

Drag the MacAddressPlugin.m and MacAddressPlugin.h to your Xcode project

add this line to the config.xml

 <plugin name="MacAddressPlugin" value="MacAddressPlugin" />

copy the MacAddressPlugin.js inside your www folder and link to it in your index.html
